OL,3,CSadistic killer who stabbed woman 60
OL,4,Ctimes faces public parole hearing
OL,6,FA sadistic killer who stabbed a woman
OL,7,F60 times during sex is to face a
OL,8,Fpublic parole hearing.
OL,10,FSteven Ling, a farm worker, was jailed
OL,11,Ffor life in December 1998 after
OL,12,Fadmitting murdering Joanne Tulip, 29,
OL,13,Fin Stamfordham, Northumberland, on
OL,14,FChristmas Day a year earlier. A charge
OL,15,Fof rape was left on file.
OL,17,FIn 2022, then-justice secretary
OL,18,FDominic Raab rejected the request to
OL,19,Ftransfer Ling to a lower security
OL,20,Fjail, overruling a recommendation made
OL,21,Fby the Parole Board earlier that year.
