OL,6,FIt was the first intervention of its
OL,7,Fkind made by Mr Raab after he promised
OL,8,Fto personally review requests to move
OL,9,Fhigh-risk offenders to open jails.
OL,11,FA Ministry of Justice (MoJ) spokesman
OL,12,Fconfirmed at the time that Mr Raab had
OL,13,Frejected Ling's move "in the interest
OL,14,Fof public protection".
OL,16,FA similar request was blocked by MoJ
OL,17,Fofficials when Ling's case came before
OL,18,Fthe Parole Board in 2020.
