OL,6,FMs Tulip's mother, Doreen Soulsby -
OL,7,Fwho reportedly called on Mr Raab to
OL,8,Fkeep Ling in a closed prison and won
OL,9,Fsupport of several MPs - told The
OL,10,FTelegraph at the time that the news
OL,11,Fwas "such a relief".
OL,13,FShe said: "All the effort has been
OL,14,Freally worthwhile. I have been
OL,15,Fcampaigning and everyone that I have
OL,16,Fspoken to cannot believe on offender
OL,17,Flike him would be released into an
OL,18,Fopen prison."
