OL,6,FLing was initially ordered to serve at
OL,7,Fleast 20 years behind bars but in 2009
OL,8,Fa High Court judge cut the minimum
OL,9,Fterm to 18 years.
OL,11,FDuring sentencing at Newcastle Crown
OL,12,FCourt, Mr Justice Potts told Ling:
OL,13,F"You inflicted appalling injuries on
OL,14,F(Ms Tulip) while you were having
OL,15,Fsexual relations with her. I'm also
OL,16,Fsatisfied that there was in your
OL,17,Fmotivation an aspiration of sadism."
OL,19,FHe added: "You will never be released
OL,20,Fso long as it is thought you
OL,21,Fconstitute a danger to women."
