OL,6,FLing will face a public parole hearing
OL,7,Fon Tuesday.
OL,9,FMembers of the press and public will
OL,10,Fbe able to watch the proceedings,
OL,11,Ftaking place in the jail where Ling is
OL,12,Fbeing held, on a live stream.
